		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top" id="forumSubject">Any suggestions?<br clear="all" /><script type="text/javascript">document.title = document.title + ": Thread: Any suggestions?";</script>
		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Thu, Dec 14th 2:52 PM2000 </span><span id="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a href="/db/classes.html?class=8&mid=9768055479607&post=1"><a class="sm" href="/db/classes.html?class=8&mid=9768055479607&num=6&page=0&post=1&replyto=9768055479607"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a></a>    <a name=9768055479607></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <span id=>Anonymous</span></a><b><span id=></span></b>
		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Default [2.00]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Anonymous&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Hi there all,<br><br>I am going to start playing Everquest and decided that I am going to play a halfling druid. What would you recommend I spend my extra ability points on? Max wis out and stamina if any points left over? Any other character creation tips would be awesome.<br><br>Thanks!<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >6 Replies</td></tr></table>
